title: About me
text:
I am a skilled mobile client engineer with around 5 years of industry experience.I have a verifiable history of contributing directly to company growth and expansion throughout my career.
I have consistently exceeded performance goals and I am adept at achieving maximum operational output with minimal resource expenditure. My current focus is on iOS development, but I have experience in android and react-native as well.
I am also highly interested in technologies that help me to make maintainable and elegant mobile application, such as MVVM pattern, reactive programming and unit test.
